ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of ANDREW DIGBY of St-Lambert, Quebec, as a member of the Great Lakes Pilotage Authority to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Ivan A. Lantz, whose term has expired.
